      <main>
        <section class="hero" id="home">
          <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Hi, I'm Dev, a product designer</h1>
            <p>I craft intuitive and engaging digital experiences that blend aesthetics with functionality. My work is driven by a passion for user-centered design and a commitment to creating impactful solutions.</p>
            <a href="#projects" class="cta-button">View Projects</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section" id="about">
          <h2>About Me</h2>
          <p>I am a passionate product designer with over 5 years of experience in creating user-centered digital products. My expertise lies in crafting intuitive and visually appealing interfaces that enhance user engagement and satisfaction. I believe in a collaborative design process, working closely with clients and stakeholders to bring their visions to life. My goal is to create designs that not only look great but also solve real-world problems and improve people's lives.</p>
        </section>

